{"iti48:0.1":"Itivuttaka 48 ","iti48:0.2":"Dukanipata ","iti48:0.3":"Dutiyavagga ","iti48:0.4":"Apayikasutta ","iti48:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti48:2.1":"“Dveme, bhikkhave, apayika nerayika idamappahaya. ","iti48:2.2":"Katame dve? ","iti48:2.3":"Yo ca abrahmacari brahmacaripatinno, yo ca paripunnam parisuddham brahmacariyam carantam amulakena abrahmacariyena anuddhamseti. ","iti48:2.4":"Ime kho, bhikkhave, dve apayika nerayika idamappahaya”ti. ","iti48:2.5":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti48:2.6":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti48:3.1":"“Abhutavadi nirayam upeti, ","iti48:3.2":"Yo vapi katva na karomi caha; ","iti48:3.3":"Ubhopi te pecca sama bhavanti, ","iti48:3.4":"Nihinakamma manuja parattha. ","iti48:4.1":"Kasavakantha bahavo, ","iti48:4.2":"papadhamma asannata; ","iti48:4.3":"Papa papehi kammehi, ","iti48:4.4":"nirayam te upapajjare. ","iti48:5.1":"Seyyo ayogulo bhutto, ","iti48:5.2":"tatto aggisikhupamo; ","iti48:5.3":"Yance bhunjeyya dussilo, ","iti48:5.4":"ratthapindamasannato”ti. ","iti48:6.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti48:6.2":"Ekadasamam. "}